---
title: Korean Tofu Rice Bowl with Sesame Veggies & Sriracha Mayo
description: If you're familiar with bibimbap, the Korean “mixed rice” dish, then you'll love this HelloFresh plant-based version. So, divvy up
the fragrant rice, pile on the tofu and toppings and then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-tofu-rice-bowl-147f1824.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/korean-tofu-rice-bowl-612838315c8dc876792a1a16-6a472e8c.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/korean-tofu-rice-bowl-612838315c8dc876792a1a16
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
